<section id="home" class="hero-section">
  <canvas id="blackhole-canvas"></canvas>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="poem">
          It does not ask permission.<br>
      <h2 class="ember-title">II. Emberborn</h2>
      <p class="subtitle"> A fire that does not yield</p>
      
      <div class="stanzas">
        <p class="stanza">
          Beneath the noise of the world,<br>
          beneath the static of every wasted hour,<br>
          there is a rhythm.<br>
          A pulse, faint but unyielding.<br>
          It does not scream.<br>
          <span class="ember-word">It burns.</span>
        </p>

        <p class="stanza">
          It is the hunger that speaks in still moments<br>
          when no one watches,<br>
          when the world forgets you.<br>
          It says:<br>
          <em>You are not done.</em>
        </p>

        <!-- <p class="stanza">
          Quiet ambition is not meek.<br>
          It is not polite.<br>
          It waits in shadows,<br>
          but it does not sleep.
        </p> -->

        <p class="stanza">
          It is the curl of smoke before the blaze,<br>
          the held breath before the leap,<br>
          the solitary candle in a room of dusk.<br>
          <span class="ember-word">Small. </span> <br>
          <span class="ember-word"> Defiant.</span>
        </p>

        <p class="stanza">
          There is a kind of fire<br>
          that doesn't need applause.<br>

          It lives in the bones of the stubborn,<br>
          in the souls of the strange.<br>
          It climbs out of cracked hearts<br>
          and walks barefoot through ruin<br>
          just to prove<br>
          that it can.
        </p>

        <p class="stanza">
          It doesn't ask,<br>
          <em>Will I make it?</em><br>
          It asks,<br>
          <em>Will I burn long enough to find out?</em>
        </p>

        <p class="stanza">
          So let them mock your pace.<br>
          Let them say you're lost.<br>
          You know better.<br>
          You know this heat<br>
          that grows in silence,<br>
          that survives rain,<br>
          that remembers every promise you ever made<br>
          to yourself.
        </p>

        <p class="stanza final-stanza">
          You are the flame no one saw coming.<br>
          You are the ember that refused to die.<br>
          You are the beat that keeps drumming<br>
          in a world too deaf to listen.<br><br>
          <span class="ember-word final-line">So burn.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-indicator">
        <p>Scroll to explore</p>
        <div class="arrow">â†“</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  #blackhole-canvas {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .poem {
    animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
  }
  
  .ember-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ff6b35;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.5);
    animation: emberGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #ff9a6b;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .stanzas {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-height: 60vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding-right: 1rem;
    scrollbar-width: thin;
    scrollbar-color: #ff6b35 transparent;
  }
  
  .stanzas::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 8px;
  }
  
  .stanzas::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: transparent;
  }
  
  .stanzas::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: #ff6b35;
    border-radius: 4px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  
  .stanzas::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
    background: #ff8c42;
  }
  
  .stanza {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    color: #e6e6e6;
    animation: stanzaFadeIn 1s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  
  .stanza:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2.5s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 3s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 3.5s; }
  .stanza:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 4s; }
  
  .ember-word {
    color: #ff4500;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.7);
    animation: emberPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .final-line {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #ff6b35;
    text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.8);
    animation: finalEmberGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  
  .final-stanza {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .stanza em {
    color: #ffb347;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .scroll-indicator p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  
  @keyframes stanzaFadeIn {
    from { 
      opacity: 0; 
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to { 
      opacity: 1; 
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes emberGlow {
    0% { 
      text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.5);
      color: #ff6b35;
    }
    100% { 
      text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.3);
      color: #ff8c42;
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes emberPulse {
    0%, 100% { 
      text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.7);
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% { 
      text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 69, 0, 1), 0 0 35px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.5);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes finalEmberGlow {
    0% { 
      text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.8);
      color: #ff6b35;
    }
    100% { 
      text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 107, 53, 1), 0 0 60px rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.6);
      color: #ff4500;
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    40% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
    60% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }
</style>

<script>
  import { BlackHoleAnimation } from '../utils/blackhole-animation.js';

  // Initialize when DOM is loaded
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    new BlackHoleAnimation('blackhole-canvas');
  });
</script>
